      "content": "The census taker seems pretty reliable though, as the records from the surrounding counties are very consistent during that same period. I also checked the local parish registers for deaths, and they don't show a spike that would account for the missing numbers. Is there anything else that could cause a significant, localized disappearance of people from the records that isn't related to death or war?",
